{"tid":928951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"🎊垃圾的花生特約：遲買貴一球🎉2014年不上車，2018年樓爆買貴一球半","createTime":"2018-12-05T08:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T09:56:40.000Z","uid":43146,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f279f7b89abfeb3c0556b750e16168ba5b85506","tid":928951,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"【交投反彈】金獅2房483萬重返年初價 4年升近五成 (12:47)<br />\n文章日期：2018年12月5日<br />\n<br />\n踏入本月，部分新界上車盤交投有反彈之勢。市場消息指，大圍金獅花園二期A座中層01室，實用面積306方呎（建築499方呎），兩房間隔，以483萬元沽出，實呎15,784元。 資料顯示，成交價重返今年屋苑同類首季樓價水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2014年以330萬元購入單位，持貨約4年，帳面獲利約153萬元，單位升值約47%。"},{"pid":"91a686e3a6db15d96049a33d351566efca0f40ad","tid":928951,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"金獅都高價追貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a83de7dacd20eda8a65f684a3f2ea8ede3f943b","tid":928951,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"833ddeb9adc7a532542c0def12ae00a3f7ba9694","tid":928951,"uid":78791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1f243ea81e67e3d282fc74ab553399216c0f14b","tid":928951,"uid":72647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"買嗰個係咪on9"},{"pid":"a79280814c021ae1e2cd911cce554ab9886f065a","tid":928951,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a83de7dacd20eda8a65f684a3f2ea8ede3f943b","tid":928951,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"一巴打柒咗青山道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff3f2e77f40be9be9734ea304041bd38c9d0600","tid":928951,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl